@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5225

### Healthy check
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/health/

### OpenApi
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json

### Get fund
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/funds/1

### Create fund
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/funds
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "name": "Global Equity Fund",
  "isin": "BE1234567890",
  "currency": "EUR"
}
